name: SnakeEyes
description:
SnakeEyes is a small scale game for me to develop as a way to practice Godot. It has since become a passion project of mine. 

Please note that the release here is only a small demo. There is much more to come for SnakeEyes and it is FAR from a complete release. I will keep on updating the game :)

I also maintain a small channel on Youtube to keep track of my progress.

https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCm-eyy9xn0z6e8sBnzop3NA

SnakeEyes will always be free to play.
